data.description: Take a look at this beautiful two story home in the Upper Valley. This spacious home sits on a huge corner with beautiful mountain views. It features 4 Bedrooms, 2.5 Baths with two living areas. As you walk in, you are welcomed by a formal living room with high ceilings. The dining room is adjacent to the kitchen which boats a kitchen island and pantry. The kitchen is open to the cozy family room which has a warm fireplace. The laundry room and a half bath are also downstairs. Upstairs you will find four spacious bedrooms, including a primary bedroom with a walk in closet. The master bath includes a double sink, garden tub, and separate walk in shower. As you walk outside to the extended patio, you will find a fully landscaped backyard with plenty of space. There is potential for RV or trailer parking on both sides of the home. The front features stone veneer in the front fascia and stamped concrete in the front porch area. The roof was recently replaced with 30 yr shingle . Take a look before it's gone!
